    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a double VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a linear 333 hp with an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral traction. This example is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative subframe reinforcement, rod bearing replacement, and a complete VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic turn-in and chassis balance this platform is renowned for. A rare, turn-key investment for the serious purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
