    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been maintained to a fastidious standard, kept in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint is entirely original, boasting a deep, glass-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, the carpets remain pristine under the original floor mats, and the interior retains its factory-fresh scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified specialists. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who accepts nothing less than perfection. Included in the sale are all original manuals, three sets of keys, and a binder containing every service receipt from new.",
