      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I am so excited to pass this beauty along to its next owner. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in stunning shape\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been babied since day one, always garage-kept and professionally detailed. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a road trip today, this is definitely the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
